featureType.name: TemperateAus_benthic_video_habitat_annotations_obs
featureType.title: Benthic annotations of 5 broad habitat classes from video observations in temperate Australia - extract from GlobalArchive
featureType.abstract: This dataset is an extract from GlobalArchive (https://globalarchive.org/) of publicly available benthic habitat annotations from stereo-BRUV drops in temperate Australia. This layer is styled according to 5 broad classes of habitat (bare consolidated, bare unconsolidated, macroalgae, seagrass, sessile invertebrates). These validation points were used as inputs to predicted benthic habitat mapping for this region. This layer has been created for use in a layer package in combination with habitat models. GlobalArchive should be used for download access, and to view more data for the region.
